title: 10 Endrathukkulla audio launch on October 6
text:
The audio launch of Vikram's upcoming film 10 Endrathukkulla will be held tomorrow (October 6). The teaser of the film directed by Vijay Milton has already created a great impact among the audience. The film's producers, Fox Star India and AR Murugadoss have announced that the audio will be out tomorrow. The film has music by Imman.
The single Vroom Vroom has already become a big hit. The film also has Vikram, Samantha Ruth Prabhu, Pasupathy, Jackie Shroff, Abhimanyu Singh as part of the star cast and is slated to release on October 21.
